title: Astoria Studio / No Fee
posting_body: ['Astoria studio on 32nd Street between Broadway and 34th Avenue.', '1/2 block to Broadway station.', 'Rent $1550 includes all utilities (gas, heat, water).', 'Private entrance, bathroom includes standing shower.', 'Kitchen w/ refrigerator, stove and sink.', 'Located on 1st floor of a 2 family house.', 'Note: You have to walk past furnace to get to the apartment.', 'The rear of the apartment is on level with backyard.', 'Access to patio is included.', 'No smokers, no pets please', 'Financial requirements: 35-40x salary, FICO > 680.', 'In-state guarantors accepted.', 'Process:', 'If you are interested, please respond to this email and I will send you a Google Form to fill out (about 5 questions) so that you can be qualified.', "Once qualified, you'll get an email to arrange for a showing.", 'There is no app fee for qualification but $30 app fee for applying for the apartment after a showing.']
